WEBVTT

00:08:59.741 --> 00:09:01.126
where you are

00:09:01.150 --> 00:09:02.789
and in your own way.

00:09:03.952 --> 00:09:06.440
We don't have to be heroes,

00:09:06.464 --> 00:09:07.771
wear a uniform,

00:09:07.795 --> 00:09:09.418
call ourselves activists

00:09:09.442 --> 00:09:11.394
or get elected to participate.

00:09:11.870 --> 00:09:15.387
We just have to be brave enough to care.

00:09:16.994 --> 00:09:21.047
Now, around the time Thelonious was born,

00:09:21.071 --> 00:09:24.769
I went to the birthday party
of a man named Gene Moretti.

00:09:26.064 --> 00:09:28.545
It was his 100th birthday,

00:09:29.955 --> 00:09:33.738
which means he lived in the United States
through the Depression, World War II,